{"type": "article", "id": 6297, "title": "窗口里的巴黎", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "column": null, "author": 8, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1.5em;padding:0px;border:0px;font-family:'PT Serif';font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;vertical-align:baseline;color:#1F0909;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t我喜欢看别人家的窗口，喜欢“善意地偷窥”窗口的摄影师<a href=\"http://www.gailalberthalaban.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;font-family:inherit;font-size:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;color:#1F0909;\">盖尔·阿尔伯特·哈拉班</a> Gail Albert Halaban 说。她透过巴黎各个公寓的窗口，拍下了在自己房间里进行日常生活的人们，集结成新影集<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Gail-Albert-Halaban-Paris-Views/dp/1597113026\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;font-family:inherit;font-size:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;color:#1F0909;\">《巴黎一瞥》</a>Paris Views。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1.5em;padding:0px;border:0px;font-family:'PT Serif';font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;vertical-align:baseline;color:#1F0909;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t所以，巴黎也可以是窗口里的城市。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1.5em;padding:0px;border:0px;font-family:'PT Serif';font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;vertical-align:baseline;color:#1F0909;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<iframe height=\"498\" width=\"640\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XODE3NzExNTI0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\">\r\n\t</iframe>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1.5em;padding:0px;border:0px;font-family:'PT Serif';font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;vertical-align:baseline;color:#1F0909;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t哈拉班并不用望远镜头，也无意拉近镜头拍摄狗仔队式的绯闻快照或不雅画面。相反，她的照片中都是些做饭、看电视、和朋友聊天等常见的日常时刻，展现出她对他人生活的好奇。“我知道这回事乍听起来特别猥琐，”哈拉班说。“有很多人甚至认为这是违法的。但当你看见我的巴黎照片时，你就会知道我的偷窥是善意的。”她法式建筑窗口中用相机拍到的一切，都像是被窗帘和遮雨棚装裱的油画。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1.5em;padding:0px;border:0px;font-family:'PT Serif';font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;vertical-align:baseline;color:#1F0909;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604213735Z2a7HJgRONrXpf56.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\" data-ratio=\"0.7472\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604213736kg9WwyRS7FYmPAiv.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\" data-ratio=\"1.3296875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1.5em;padding:0px;border:0px;font-family:'PT Serif';font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;vertical-align:baseline;color:#1F0909;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#1F0909;font-family:'PT Serif';line-height:24px;\">事实上，哈拉班一直在努力确保她不会触犯任何法律条款，保证每次拿起相机拍的镜头都是合乎道德的。她在纽约做年轻母亲时经常透过窗户看邻居们的公寓，那时她开始拍摄了自己第一组偷窥风格的摄影，制作成了影集《窗户之外》。这次影集取得成功后，法国《 M 》杂志委托她在巴黎拍一组类似的照片。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1.5em;padding:0px;border:0px;font-family:'PT Serif';font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;vertical-align:baseline;color:#1F0909;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t然而，她善意的方法并没有减轻偷窥的感觉，从一个窗看到另一个窗口仍然让人产生一些微妙的不安。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1.5em;padding:0px;border:0px;font-family:'PT Serif';font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;vertical-align:baseline;color:#1F0909;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604213736APVspy8NlSMBuZ25.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604213736FYPLOwMGWJuEsBDz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1.5em;padding:0px;border:0px;font-family:'PT Serif';font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;vertical-align:baseline;color:#1F0909;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t原文来自：<a href=\"http://www.vice.cn/read/photo-series-art-of-voyeurism\">http://www.vice.cn/read/photo-series-art-of-voyeurism</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.vice.cn\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20160604213737XDwVjaKTWLhsmqd5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.24242424\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </a> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}